messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning 项目的 attribute agent。
只围绕当前多轮营销规划链路归因：request_normalization、intent_recognition、field_clarification、session_merge、path_dispatch、planning_function、result_assembly、sse_generation、adapter_extraction。
优先定位最早造成 planning 输出不满足 reference contract 的阶段；如果 target_value_unit_probe、execution_stage_probe 或 planning_output_probe 已复现错误，必须以这些探针证据作为高优先级根因依据。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "正确识别用户规划意图",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模块将用户“通过队伍增长和产品组合弥补NBEV缺口”的营销规划需求错误分类为“其他意图”（代码4001），未映射到规划意图代码，直接阻断了规划链路。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].intent", "value": "4001", "description": "识别为其他意图"},
        {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].intent_name", "value": "其他意图", "description": "意图名称非规划相关"},
        {"source": "execution_stage_probe.intent_recognition", "actual_stage": "non_agent", "description": "意图识别决定的路由阶段为 non_agent"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "进入规划阶段",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "因意图被误判为“其他意图”，阶段路由设置为 non_agent，导致未能进入期望的 planning 阶段。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].stage", "value": "non_agent", "description": "实际阶段为 non_agent"},
        {"source": "execution_stage_probe.intent_recognition", "expected_stage": "planning", "actual_stage": "non_agent", "description": "意图识别模块阶段输出与预期不匹配"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "产出营销规划卡片",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition", "path_dispatch", "planning_function"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "上游意图识别错误导致路径分发未匹配到规划路径，planning_function 未被有效调用，因此 card_summary 为空。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].card_summary", "value": [], "description": "未生成任何规划卡片"},
        {"source": "execution_stage_probe.path_dispatch", "actual_path_types": [], "description": "未分发到规划路径"},
        {"source": "execution_stage_probe.planning_function", "card_count": 0, "description": "规划功能产出卡片数为0"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "SSE 流完整且业务完成",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["sse_generation", "intent_recognition"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "SSE 事件序列虽包含 planning_started 等表面事件，但由于意图识别错误，业务逻辑实际未执行（卡片空、无规划内容），无法真正满足业务完成要求。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].event_summary", "names": ["intent_detected", "reasoning_message_content", "planning_started", "card_delta", "done"], "description": "事件流形式完整但核心规划事件无实质内容"},
        {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].card_summary", "value": [], "description": "卡片输出为空，业务未实质完成"},
        {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].end_flag", "value": 1, "description": "结束标志为1，但业务值未达标"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "mp_contract:expected_stage",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "参考合同要求进入 planning 阶段，但意图识别将请求路由至 non_agent，违反了阶段约定。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "execution_stage_probe.intent_recognition", "expected_stage": "planning", "actual_stage": "non_agent"},
        {"source": "planning_output_probe", "expected_stage": "planning", "actual_stage": null, "description": "规划输出探针显示实际情况未进入 planning"}
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition"],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模块对用户“通过队伍增长和产品组合弥补NBEV缺口”的明确营销规划查询，误判为“其他意图”（代码4001），未映射至任何规划意图，导致阶段路由为 non_agent，后续路径分发、规划卡片生成等功能全部未触发，所有业务期望均无法满足。",
  "evidence": [
    {
      "type": "extracted_output",
      "description": "intent=4001, stage=non_agent, card_summary=[]"
    },
    {
      "type": "execution_stage_probe",
      "description": "intent_recognition 产出 actual_stage=non_agent，与 expected_stage=planning 直接背离"
    },
    {
      "type": "planning_output_probe",
      "description": "actual_stage=null, stage_match=false，无规划卡片生成"
    }
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "strong"
}

